Minneapolis-St. Paul 35 fair; Nashville 38 fair; New Orleans 59
fair; St. Louis 42 fair.
   _West: Albuquerque 58 windy; Anchorage 32 fair; Las Vegas 67
fair; Los Angeles 76 fair; Phoenix 78 fair; Salt Lake City 52 fair;
San Diego 74 fair; San Francisco 66 fair; Seattle 49 foggy.
   _Canada: Montreal 45 cloudy; Toronto 39 foggy.
